text: Domenico Pinelli, seniore (1541–1611) was a Roman Catholic cardinal. ==Episcopal succession== While bishop, he was the principal consecrator of: and the principal co-consecrator of: *Pedro de Deza Manuel, Bishop of Albano (1600); and *Lanfranco Margotti, Bishop of Viterbo e Tuscania (1609). ==References== Category:1541 births Category:1611 deaths Category:Cardinals (Catholic Church)
title: Domenico Pinelli
